<keyLead box="[136,1451,1220,1242]" pageId="8" pageNumber="81">4. Basidiomes subfragile, reddish brown when dry; basal mycelium absent........................................................................................ 5</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[136,1451,986,1473]" box="[136,1451,1249,1271]" pageId="8" pageNumber="81">
<keyLead box="[136,1451,1249,1271]" pageId="8" pageNumber="81">4. Basidiomes more robust, pale yellow when dry; basal mycelium present.........................................................................................6</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="8" pageNumber="81">
